onsidered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other drugs that are also associated with these adverse effects.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/45877/', '', 'Pertuzumab, Rucaparib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Enasidenib, Mitotane, Porfimer sodium, Aflibercept, Trastuzumab, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
