ther hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/45887/', '', 'Pertuzumab, Olaparib, Rucaparib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Altretamine, Enasidenib, Porfimer sodium, Niraparib, Selinexor, More', 'Tiagabine, Ethotoin, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Methsuximide, Zonisamide, Lamotrigine, Ganaxolone, Fenfluramine, More', 1767369485);
